Use the standard library
This is how to filter_integers of values:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this values's length times:
      When isint of item i in values is yes, then:
         Add result to item i in values
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know

>>> filter_integers of [5]
[5]
>>> filter_integers of [1, 2, 3]
[1, 2, 3]
>>> filter_integers of []
[]